{"tid":601821,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"【氣象】（2018年3月下旬）旬初天氣晴朗早上清涼，中期雲量轉多，旬末有霧","createTime":"2018-03-22T13:40:03.000Z","updateTime":"2018-03-25T09:52:39.000Z","uid":44630,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"4976acb2b6b80fdac1dcecd9ffca0ab20488e193","tid":601821,"uid":44630,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-22T13:40:03.000Z","msg":"<strong><span style=\"color: green;\"><img src=\"http://imgur.com/fxgjJzQ.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimgur.com%2FfxgjJzQ.png&h=e15d1b57&s={SIZE}\" /> <span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><ins>氣象討論：2018年3月下旬</ins></span></span><br />\n<span style=\"color: limegreen;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">此帖文討論期：2018年3月21日至31日</span></span></strong><br />\n【註】 氣象討論帖一般逢每月1日、11日及21日發出新帖文。　當新帖文發出後，或有颱風追擊帖發出，原有的氣象討論帖會隨即停用。　為使大家有一個良好舒適的瀏覽環境，請不要使用簡體中文貼文、提及力場或洗版，謝謝合作。<br />\n<strong><em><span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">氣象台專頁現已登場</span><br />\n<img src=\"http://x.co/FBlike\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fx.co%2FFBlike&h=5fdd3157&s={SIZE}\" /><a href=\"http://fb.com/HKGweather\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Ffb.com%2FHKGweather&d=vmp%2BLbkGsXc7YfaF1kid1MPrXSGIZiPsBFv3mRhlVuk%3D&h=8730f1c2\" target=\"_blank\">http://fb.com/HKGweather</a><br />\n<img src=\"http://x.co/TWlike\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fx.co%2FTWlike&h=e9b064ef&s={SIZE}\" /><a href=\"http://twitter.com/HKGweather\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FHKGweather&d=vmp%2BLbkGsXc7YfaF1kid1MPrXSGIZiPsBFv3mRhlVuk%3D&h=93020b5b\" target=\"_blank\">http://twitter.com/HKGweather</a></span></em><br />\n<img src=\"http://i.imgur.com/BZfpfrS.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2FBZfpfrS.png&h=9df3da65&s={SIZE}\" /><a href=\"http://youtube.com/HKGweather\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F